this is interesting, however, i feel no guilt, rather pride in my choise to go to canada. as a 11b10. jan 68  i was sittin in a baracks in ft lewis waitin to get on a plane, and instead, hitched to canada for 7 years...then the fun..the return..what a story....maybe later<br><br>
